This is a proof of concept demo of MediaPlayer (MP) plugin. 
The MP plugin is designed to play mixed media playlists.

In this demo the MP plugin have be combined with the taglist plugin (and some other plugins) to enable playlist to be constructed using drag and drop.

See the [[demo tiddler|PlayLists]]. The working are outlined [[here|Architecture]].